{
  "stem": "3022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we made the decision not to go to the main railway station, but to go to a minor station.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the German soldiers wouldn't be there and they wouldn't be checking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We set out at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a, a full moon, completely cloudless night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were on this sled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the, the wolves from the forest which we were passing by scared the horses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the sled went into the ditch, and we couldn't dig out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at night, the landscape was something like you see in winter landscape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's what it looked like.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nothing-- you could see nothing but snow and the moon shining.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We finally found a little hut where a Polish peasant helped us out and pulled out this sled out on the road.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went to the train station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When we got on the train, 10 minutes later, some German gendarmes came over and confiscated all the food that we had with us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was one of the reasons also that we decided to get out from Cracow and go into a smaller town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Eventually, as I said, my mother moved to the town of Zawichost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at that time, the, the Germans ceased-- you know, they didn't give my father the permits or the orders to buy the-- they completely excluded the, the Jewish previous owners.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because a ghetto was being formed in Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and my father lost the contact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he had to look for some other means of support.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Since he was the only kosher butcher in that little town that we lived in who was willing to, to risk his freedom and life and slaughter, and slaughter, which was illegal, he engaged into, in the butchering.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This is what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
